# React + TypeScript Conventions

- TS config should use `"jsx": "react-jsx"` (already set in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)).
- After migration to React 18, update entry to `createRoot` in [src/index.tsx](mdc:src/index.tsx).
- Import `RootState` from [src/typescript/types.ts](mdc:src/typescript/types.ts) when using `useSelector`.
- If JSX intrinsic errors occur, ensure `@types/react` and `@types/react-dom` versions align with React version.
